{"tid":1316442,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[自由討論] 經歷上水沙田兩役，如何升級?","createTime":"2019-07-14T16:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T17:06:25.000Z","uid":272057,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"55b86d5bf5df3e638e831786f2349a2545ec556a","tid":1316442,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:02:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>經歷上水沙田兩役，自由討論如何再進一步</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">我篇嘢嘅全文大意:想更多人覺醒，想有革命，好簡單，買一百支地拖棍</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">進步=令更多人清醒</span>       <br />\n  <span style=\"color: green;\">方法=狗打市民+義士自己升級</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我講先啦，要開始升級裝備，遮已經同紙無分別，<span style=\"color: maroon;\">大家將裝備由傘upgrade做長棍，令你同狗嘅武力對等</span>，下一次喺game入面同狗對峙，希望最少有五十人拎住實木地拖棍，(記住唔好自己基地帶去，好易被狗查cctv捉到)，長棍可以幫你同狗保持距離，有人被人捉嗰陣，有長棍嘅又可以幫手隔開隻狗，唔使自己行埋去，啱晒錫身嘅香港人。而棍又唔會造成他人流血，唔會俾和理非屌。</span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">我知第一次係會少人咁做，但呢種輕暴力升級會令更多人接受，藍絲都唔會話棍大殺傷力，因為班狗都用，相信之後嘅示威會越來越多人用棍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但大家要知，當武力對等，狗就會自動升級武力，當有學生中槍，世人會聯想起六四，示威者被逼再升級，成件事最終會演變成革命，我只擔心一樣嘢，就係香港人身心未準備好。</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真心想做嘅話，就721喺附近買地拖棍拎去物資站，你唔用都好，買俾勇武保護你。</span><br />\n<br />\nbtw 文宣組睇下條片啱唔啱用，希望可以激起更多人革命嘅決心<br />\n[ <em><span style=\"color: teal;\">香港需要嘅唔係一棟建築，而係希望！</span></em> ]<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZYSaYrbffbg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZYSaYrbffbg&d=LzMeHrLekQtOmJ7gjClTQBZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=45fc94d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZYSaYrbffbg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>以下開放自由討論</strong></span>"},{"pid":"2665f2121d3803265a0d3e9d93e1c9db50b46da9","tid":1316442,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:02:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9d70278061851330f1aafb74ab7e6519496f539","tid":1316442,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:03:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45ea893d8714b0ab9be3d3940c4feff3c42df173","tid":1316442,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:03:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c0cf6184b26428ca58b419ff6992a9330400210","tid":1316442,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:03:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"230ee1df02af93a0d9e9b95e05f36dfcf83d97d2","tid":1316442,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:03:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"391727605bb45f773ca29006b1282637a42c938f","tid":1316442,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:03:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ddc7c515f5177d477d0df8000d7266407fc6b239","tid":1316442,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:04:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dee21f1b479145f5e1581da8b999bdb4d3fa6d8a","tid":1316442,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:04:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"217ac52e6b0f0b867d39065dca20c01371f2c571","tid":1316442,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉"},{"pid":"d6ac8762c379762526f1d39c0d753c287ad3deb3","tid":1316442,"uid":168214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:07:01.000Z","msg":"十大武器之首都無人提過<br />\n摺凳啊屌你<br />\n<br />\n返去睇多啲國產零零柒啦"},{"pid":"d3036a2a01d9fb26a4701e4f7d3085f7e48082d5","tid":1316442,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:14:17.000Z","msg":"打死人咩 點可以禁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2760f1760975e635aac52f8e3370f8c9ce87fd33","tid":1316442,"uid":258192,"like":0,"